      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "With his princes.—Captains (‘im sārāv); Kings, “to Zair,” which appears to be a corruption of “to Seir.” The chronicler has substituted an intelligible for an obscure expression.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "With his princes.",
